'''Spookality 2025''' is an iteration of an annual [[wikipedia:Halloween|Halloween]]-themed VRChat [[Special:MyLanguage/Events|event]]. A [[Special:MyLanguage/World|world]] and [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatars|avatar]] jam were announced, alongside details<ref name="SpookalityAsk">[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/spookality-2025-jam "Spookality 2025 Jam!"] on ''[[ask.vrchat.com]]''. Dated September 17, 2025. Retrieved September 17, 2025.</ref> for the jam.

==Overview==
Spookality 2025 marks the 9th edition of the event, and like previous years, a world and avatar jam accompanying it. The post announcing the event went live on September 17th, 2025, describing all details, rules and prizes. Within the post, included an "opening sequence".

