==Details==

===Dates===
Submissions for the jam began on September 22nd, 2025 and closed on October 13th, 2025. Submissions were being judged for the next couple days. The winners of the jam were announced on October 22nd.  

===Theme===
====Avatars====
The theme of this jam is:<ref name="SpookalityAsk" />

* '''Analog Horror'''

Submissions will be judged in the following categories:

* Performance: Must be Medium or better on all platforms (PC, Android, and iOS) 
* Style / Aesthetics: Is this a good-looking avatar?
* Extra Features: Bonus points for face tracking, desktop arm, etc.

In addition to the judging criteria, all submissions are required to be [[Special:MyLanguage/Platforms|cross-platform]] (PC, Android & iOS), and must be uploaded after the start of the jam.

====Worlds====
The theme of this jam is:

* '''Shifting Shadows'''
** Create short, replayable horror experiences that never unfold the same way twice.

Submissions will be judged in the following categories:

* Replayability: How replayable is this world? Is it fun to play or explore multiple times in a row?
* Technical Execution: Is this world free of technical bugs?
* Horror / Spooky theme: Was this world thematic for Halloween? 
* Overall Experience

In addition to the judging criteria, all submissions are required to be cross-platform (PC, Android & iOS), and must be uploaded after the start of the jam.

===Prizes===
[[File:Badge Spookality Jam (2025).png|200px|thumb|The Spookality Jam (2025) badge.]]
The prize for the avatar category winners are:<ref name="SpookalityRules">[https://hello.vrchat.com/spookality-2025-rules "VRCHAT SPOOKALITY 2025 CONTEST"] on ''[[hello.vrchat.com]]''. Dated September 17, 2025. Retrieved September 18, 2025.</ref>

* Top 10 avatars receive:
** A one-year gift subscription to VRC+ (split up to 4 people, if on a team.)
** Spookality 2025 [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]]
** Fast-tracked into the [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatar Marketplace|Avatar Marketplace]] Seller Program (if they’re not already in it)
***Featured in a special Avatar Marketplace row.

The prize for the world category winners are:

* Top 10 worlds receive:
** A one-year gift subscription to VRC+ (split up to 4 people, if on a team.)
** Spookality 2025 badge
** Fast-tracked into the [[Special:MyLanguage/Creator Economy|Creator Economy]] program (if they’re not already in it)
** World Row feature

All other winners will be considered to be featured in the Spookality World Row – although they will be featured after the top 10 winners.

